      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E92 M3, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit features a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for superior lateral dynamics. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including updated rod bearings and throttle actuators, ensuring the integrity of the high-tension valvetrain. The chassis maintains its composure via Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and refreshed subframe bushings, providing sharp turn-in and high-speed stability. While the exterior shows minor road rash on the front apron, the Interlagos Blue finish remains vibrant. This is a driver-spec example with a linear power band that pulls hard to its 8,400 RPM redline.",
