      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver that balances performance with comfort. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, showing only minimal cosmetic wear such as light stone chips on the front bumper and a small, faint scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014imperfections that are hardly noticeable from a distance. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The leather upholstery is in great shape, with only minor creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster and firm cushioning throughout. All electronic components, including the infotainment system, dual-zone climate control, and driver-assist features, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is sound; it has a consistent service history, with a recent fluid flush and brake inspection completed last month. The engine idles quietly, and the transmission delivers smooth, reliable shifts. It sits on a set of premium tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a dependable, aesthetically pleasing vehicle that is ready for the road today.",
